Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:05.36,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I wondered if your name has anything to do with R. D. Laing. Oh, it couldn’t, could it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.52,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,R.D. Laing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:08.64,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It’s a person’s name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.34,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,An English psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:12.96,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,He was an unusual person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:16.52,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,The titles of some of his books are very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.44,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,One of them is: “I Love, Love, Really Love.”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:21.68,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,“I Love, Love, Really Love”?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:34.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I read it when I was in college and I don’t remember much of it, but it’s about two lovers—a man and a woman—and the woman asks the man if he loves her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:36.20,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:39.62,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Well of course, the man replies that he loves her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:44.18,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But the woman isn't satisfied, and asks more and more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:45.70,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:50.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,OK. Let’s see. Do you like me, Lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:52.58,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:55.32,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,More than your dad? More than your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:56.62,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:58.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,That makes me happy. Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:00.18,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:02.84,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Are you happy when you’re here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:06.86,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t really understand, but I probably am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.34,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Do you like talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:10.48,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.40,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What do you like about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:17.48,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,You’re kind and you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:22.02,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Which do you like more? That I’m kind, or that I listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:23.52,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Which?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:25.16,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Yes, which?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:27.16,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I like you because you’re kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.42,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,How am I kind to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.38,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,You don’t get angry and you’re polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.22,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But there are lots of people besides me who don’t get angry at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.72,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,There are lots of people who are polite to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:39.72,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Aren’t there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:42.88,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Do you really like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.24,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:47.84,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Do I have to think about all this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:49.70,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Let’s stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.84,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I feel like I might start to not like you.
